title: Boy II Men.1998.I WILL GET THERE[Mp3].256Kbps.-ROSTROMASCARADO
description:
"I Will Get There" is a single recorded by Boyz II Men in 1998 for the soundtrack of the DreamWorks animated film The Prince of Egypt. The track spent forty-one days on the Billboard Hot 100 chart, and, as of April 2011, remains to be the group's final Top 40 hit.

The song was written by Diane Warren and produced by Jimmy Jam, Terry Lewis, and Boyz II Men. The group sings the song a cappella for the recording, which peacked at number thirty-two on the Hot 100 when released as a single.
